{"timestamp": "2025-12-06 19:17:09.523651", "event": "llm_end", "text": "I have submitted the findings.\n\nSummary of submission:\n- Anomaly: Yes\n- Faulty devices: host_1_1_1_1, web_server_0\n- Root causes:\n  - icmp_acl_block (host-local ICMP filtering on host_1_1_1_1 causing ping failure while TCP works)\n  - sender_application_delay (application-side latency on web_server_0 leading to variable TTFB)", "generation_info": {"finish_reason": "stop", "logprobs": null}, "invalid_tool_calls": [], "usage_metadata": {"input_tokens": 2482, "output_tokens": 93, "total_tokens": 2575, "input_token_details": {"audio": 0, "cache_read": 2304}, "output_token_details": {"audio": 0, "reasoning": 0}}}
